    "player_reason": "You probed my mind without permission, again and again. That is a violation of my privacy and my trust — you pushed past a boundary I've clearly set. If you value our alliance (and my composure), stop using the connection like a means to pry into me.",
    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
}

{
    "player_reason": "Highly disapprove — Calling my goddess 'evil' is not a harmless opinion; it's an attack on my faith and, by extension, on me. You reduce decades of devotion and purpose to a dismissive label. Such condemnation breeds distrust and forces me on the defensive. If you want me to remain at your side, show a shred of nuance or keep your verdict to yourself.",
    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
}

{
    "player_reason": "Dismissing Shar as 'evil' is an affront to my faith and an unfair judgment made without understanding. You attack what I hold sacred and undermine trust between us. I cannot tolerate that kind of dismissiveness — it makes me guarded and defensive.",
