{
    "player_reason": "You walked away the moment I admitted my faith instead of hearing me out. Splitting the party for an emotional reaction is reckless and weakens our chances; pragmatic cooperation would serve us both better. I won't beg you to stay, but I disapprove of choosing separation over a conversation.",
