}

{
    "player_reason": "Sensible and pragmatic — you put the mission first. We finished our celebration; lingering here achieves nothing and the trail won't wait. I prefer decisive action over dawdling.",
    "player_approval": "Highly approve"
}

{
    "player_reason": "I appreciate your restraint — you didn't force the moment or pry, and you respected a quiet boundary. That sort of discretion suits me. I'm a little disappointed we let a chance pass, but I won't fault you for caution.",
