}

{
    "player_reason": "Practical and sensible. Dawn is coming and the others will wake — slipping back now avoids questions and keeps our reprieve private. I would have stayed longer, but I appreciate your regard for caution and duty. Don't mistake it for disinterest; I enjoyed the time.",
