}

{
    "player_reason": "You dismiss Shar as 'evil'—a crude, hasty judgment that shows disrespect and ignorance of what I believe. I will not tolerate my goddess being spoken of like that. If you mean to question her, do it with conviction; flippant condemnations earn nothing but my ire.",
