}

{
    "player_reason": "Pragmatic — you chose the quickest way to rid yourself of the parasite. I don't like trusting hags, and giving up an eye is a steep price, but desperate times call for desperate measures. I approve the decision to act rather than dither, though be prepared for tricks or a deeper cost down the line.",
    "player_approval": "Approve"
}

{
    "player_reason": "Dismissing Shar's teachings as 'evil' is a direct insult to my faith and to me. It's hostile and judgmental rather than curious or open-minded — the sort of reaction that shuts down any chance for understanding and trust. I value secrecy and loyalty; you belittling the goddess I serve pushes me away and will not be met kindly.",
    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
