{
    "player_reason": "You're blunt and honest about your feelings. I dislike being pried into, and if you truly cannot trust me, travelling separately keeps you from pressing me further. It's unfortunate — I would prefer allies at my back — but I respect a practical choice to avoid needless conflict. Don't expect me to beg you to stay.",
