{
    "player_reason": "You dismiss Shar's work as 'evil' — a blunt, moralistic insult that attacks my faith and betrays a shallow understanding of what we do. I will not take kindly to having my goddess and my purpose belittled. Your judgment is naive and disrespectful.",
