}

{
    "player_reason": "Cold and abrupt. You heard the truth and immediately sever ties instead of discussing it. Secrecy is central to who I am — I admitted my worship of Shar when pressed. Walking away so quickly is rash and endangers us both; a pragmatic solution would be to talk this through, not scatter the party. I do not like being shunned for being honest, even if the honesty was late.",
