{
    "player_reason": "Pragmatic, if ugly. You're willing to accept a painful, personal cost to deal with the tadpole — it may well be effective, and I respect decisive solutions — but hags are liars and that price is humiliating and dangerous. Be certain you understand the consequences before you hand yourself over.",
