{
    "player_reason": "You refuse to trust me and choose to travel alone rather than face danger with allies. I expected caution — I did warn you to be discreet — but this is short-sighted and insulting. Abandoning the party out of fear or prejudice against my worship of Shar is reckless. We are both safer together; your decision wounds me and reveals little faith in your own judgment.",
