}

{
    "player_reason": "I highly disapprove. Your abrupt decision to abandon trust over something I asked be kept private is petty and short-sighted. I've been honest when I needed to be and asked for discretion; pushing me away accomplishes nothing but weakens us both and jeopardises whatever goal we might have. If you truly think separation is safer, suit yourself — but know that I will not look kindly on being cast out for exercising caution and faith.",
    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
